{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "call",
    "params": {
        "service": "object",
        "method": "execute_kw",
        "args": [
            "{{db_name}}",
            {{user_id}},
            "{{pass}}",
            "ni.patient", // Model name e.g. res.users,
            "search_read", // Method to call e.g. "search_read","create", "write"(update), "unlink"("delete")
            [
                [], // filter domain empty array [] to get all record
                [
                    "name",
                    "title",
                    "identification_id",
                    "gender",
                    "birthdate",
                    "deceased_date",
                    "age",
                    "phone",
                    "mobile",
                    "create_date",
                    "create_uid",
                    "write_date",
                    "write_uid"
                ] //fields name to read - empty array[] to get all fields
            ],
            {"limit": 80, "offset": 2, "order": "birthdate"}
        ]
    },
    "id": {{$randomInt}} //request id for reference
}
